Question: One image contains no more than two short-haired guinea pigs posed on a blue surface, and the other image shows a single long-haired brown-and-white guinea pig.

Reference Answer: True

Left image URL: https://i.ytimg.com/vi/9ilNN59fCqs/hqdefault.jpg

Right image URL: https://i.pinimg.com/736x/2a/31/b2/2a31b2dbbbe9a337a95bf0bcb8f9b496--cute-guinea-pigs-fluffy-guinea-pigs.jpg

Program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many short-haired guinea pigs are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many long-haired guinea pigs are in the image?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the guinea pig posed on a blue surface?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the guinea pig posed on a blue surface?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} <= 2 and {ANSWER2}')
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} == 1 and {ANSWER3}')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER4} and {ANSWER5}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
